def get_delta(matrix, group_option):
    in_group_sum = 0
    in_group_count = 0
    out_group_sum = 0
    out_group_count = 0
    
    for i in range(matrix.shape[0]):
        for j in range(matrix.shape[1]):
            if check_in_group(group_option, i, j):
                in_group_sum += matrix[i][j]
                in_group_count += 1
            else:
                out_group_sum += matrix[i][j]
                out_group_count += 1
    
    in_group_avg = in_group_sum / in_group_count if in_group_count else 0
    out_group_avg = out_group_sum / out_group_count if out_group_count else 0
    
    delta = in_group_avg - out_group_avg
    return delta
